name: Warung Senja
address: 6HCF+HFQ, Tanglad, Nusa Penida, Klungkung Regency, Bali 80771, Indonesia
review 1: Good place for closing our trip with local food and sunset view ,high recomand
review 2: Very tasty nasi and mie goreng. Beautiful views and peaceful setting
review 3: Good place! People are very friendly and we had a nice lunch + nice view ! :)
review 4: Small warung at the very top of the mountain. You can watch the sun set into the sea between the mountains from there which is absolutely stunning. The whole area has amazing lookout points during daylight as well. The menu is very small, but had vegetarian and non vegetarian options. The food is delicious and very cheap and the staff is very friendly.
review 5: A small place for spending the time and try local food after arrounding east land

name: Warung Paris
address: 6HCF+HFQ, Tanglad, Nusa Penida, Klungkung Regency, Bali 80771, Indonesia
review 1: Cute little place close to teletubbies hill. Very nice people and food. Would recommend if passing. Also there is a little shop for snacks and drinks.
review 2: Mie goreng tastes good. Also a very nice pit stop when you are hungry
review 3:
Very nice food.
